OL,3,CReport damning of state failures to
OL,4,Cprevent abuse at notorious detention
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FAn inquiry into one of the most
OL,8,Fdisturbing scandals in British justice
OL,9,Fhistory has revealed that the abuse of
OL,10,Fhundreds - if not thousands - of young
OL,11,Finmates at a detention centre could
OL,12,Fhave been prevented if many in power
OL,13,Fhad acted.
OL,15,FPrisons and Probation Ombudsman Adrian
OL,16,FUsher has compiled a 202-page report
OL,17,Finto the conduct of staff at the now
OL,18,Fnotorious Medomsley Detention Centre
OL,19,Fwhich operated in County Durham from
OL,20,F1961 to 1987.
