OL,3,CReport damning of state failures to
OL,4,Cprevent abuse at notorious detention
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FPublished on Wednesday (12 November),
OL,8,Fthe report is damning of the state's
OL,9,Ffailures to prevent systematic abuse
OL,10,Fand for allowing one of the UK's most
OL,11,Fprolific sexual predators to select
OL,12,Fvictims at will.
OL,14,FPart of the inquiry focused on officer
OL,15,FNeville Husband who was described by
OL,16,FMr Usher "as possibly the most
OL,17,Fprolific sex offender in British
OL,18,Fhistory".
