OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"Husband used this power with
OL,8,Fdevastating effect."
OL,10,FThe inquiry found successive wardens
OL,11,Fat the detention centre were either
OL,12,Fcomplicit or incompetent.
OL,14,FIt reveals staff were left to decide
OL,15,Fhow the centre operated as its
OL,16,Fobjectives were not clearly set out.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@TO]
