OL,4,Cprevent abuse at notorious detention
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThe ethos of the "short, sharp shock"
OL,8,Ffor men aged 17-21, who had been
OL,9,Fconvicted of relatively minor crimes,
OL,10,Fwas in place to deter them from re-
OL,11,Foffending, and the experience was
OL,12,Fmeant to be unpleasant.
OL,14,FMr Usher said: "Such an environment
OL,15,Fmeant that some staff believed,
OL,16,Fwhatever the rule book said, that they
OL,17,Fcould best achieve their aims with
OL,18,Fviolence as a training method."
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@eO]vD@POUzD@_O]
