OL,3,CReport damning of state failures to
OL,4,Cprevent abuse at notorious detention
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThe scale of the abuse meant its
OL,8,Fleaders, known as wardens until the
OL,9,Fterm changed to governor in the 1980s,
OL,10,Fwere aware of it and therefore
OL,11,F"complicit", or "they lacked
OL,12,Fdedication and professional curiosity
OL,13,Fto such an extent as to not be
OL,14,Fprofessionally competent", the
OL,15,Fombudsman said.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@KO]sD@QOUvD@YO]
