OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FHe added: "Ultimately, they had the
OL,8,Fpower and authority to take action and
OL,9,Fprevent the abuse of hundreds, if not
OL,10,Fthousands, of victims had they
OL,11,Fdiligently and proactively discharged
OL,12,Fthe duties of their office.
OL,14,F"Sadly for the lives of those victims,
OL,15,Fthere is no evidence that they did so."
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@AOUwD@gO]
