OL,3,CReport damning of state failures to
OL,4,Cprevent abuse at notorious detention
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThe PPO found that trainees were
OL,8,Fphysically abused from the moment they
OL,9,Farrived, when they bathed, strip
OL,10,Fsearched, during physical education,
OL,11,Fwhilst working and even during medical
OL,12,Fexaminations.
OL,14,FVictims were targeted for being
OL,15,Fperceived as gay or weak.
OL,17,FInmates who failed to address staff as
OL,18,F"Sir" would be punched.
OL,20,FBaths were either scalding hot or
OL,21,Ffreezing cold, witnesses said.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@EO]
