OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FHe said: "The abuse at Medomsley
OL,8,Fcontinued, unchallenged, for the
OL,9,Fentire 26 years of its operation.
OL,11,F"The knowledge of abuse by the Prison
OL,12,FService, the police, the Home Office
OL,13,Fand other organisations of authority
OL,14,Fwas ignored and dismissed.
OL,16,F"Sending these young men to Medomsley
OL,17,Fwas supposed to instil them with more
OL,18,Fordered, law-abiding lives.
OL,20,F"The authorities failed in their duty
OL,21,Fto keep detainees safe."
