OL,7,FHe said the victims have yet to
OL,8,Freceive an official apology.
OL,10,FAddressing them, he said: "The effects
OL,11,Fof the trauma they suffered
OL,12,Feffectively became a life sentence...
OL,13,Fwith devastating consequences.
OL,15,F"However, it is my fervent hope that,
OL,16,Ffor many victims, what this report
OL,17,Frepresents is a victory for your
OL,18,Ftenacity, determination and courage.
OL,26,@rD@[OUwD@AOU
