OL,7,F"You may have had to overcome
OL,8,Fseemingly insurmountable obstacles
OL,9,Fover the last 40 years and more but,
OL,10,Fin the end, you were heard, and you
OL,11,Fwere believed."
OL,13,FThe inquiry spoke to 79 victims and
OL,14,Fwitnesses.
OL,16,FMore than 2,000 former inmates came
OL,17,Fforward to give their testimony to
OL,18,FOperation Seabrook, a police
OL,19,Finvestigation which led to five
OL,20,Fretired officers being convicted of
OL,21,Fabuse in 2019.
